query:
UPDATE services SET
                code = COALESCE(?, code),
                name = COALESCE(?, name),
                description = COALESCE(?, description),
                default_price = COALESCE(?, default_price),
                estimated_time = COALESCE(?, estimated_time),
                default_warranty_days = COALESCE(?, default_warranty_days),
                is_active = COALESCE(?, is_active),
                updated_at = ?
            WHERE id = ?
